	<div id="tab1" class="tab-content"><d><b><center>General;</center> </d> <br> <b>moniker; Jozif
 <br><b>nickname; None
	 <br><b>age; 24
	 <br><b>height; 1.85m 
	 <br><b>weight; 100kg
	 <br><b>occupation;</b><span class="marker" title="servant of the Zimnyye Nauki, an ancient order of assassins celebrating bloodshed in the name of their deity.">Assassin </span>
